  "format": "The January movie auction: three hosts split $1,000 apiece across five 2025 releases, working under Chris's category triggers — two $100M domestic grossers, an 85 Metascore, at least two Oscar nominations, no more than two sequels. First they tally how last year's slates actually paid off, then bid.",
