              "note": "Boyle and Garland's third '28' film; Ralph Fiennes in the cast. A boys-night bidding war."
            },
            {
              "title": "Eddington",
              "year": 2025,
              "price": 204,
              "note": "Ari Aster's contemporary Western, little known about it beyond the cast."
            },
            {
              "title": "A Big Bold Beautiful Journey",
              "year": 2025,
              "price": 50,
              "note": "Kogonada's first since After Yang; Margot Robbie and Colin Farrell. A May release, so unavailable next round."
            },
            {
              "title": "One Battle After Another",
              "year": 2025,
              "price": 1,
              "note": "Auctioned under its working title, The Battle of Baktan Cross. Paul Thomas Anderson; five of his films clear an 85 Metascore."
