              "price": 300,
              "note": "Mark Anthony Green's A24 debut; Ayo Edebiri and John Malkovich. She spent up because she wanted it."
            },
            {
              "title": "F1",
              "year": 2025,
              "price": 256,
              "note": "Joseph Kosinski's racing movie, one of the most expensive ever made; a June release, so gone by July."
